data.meta_description: Maximilian von Liechtenstein was born on July 25, 1641, son of Hartmann V Prinz von und zu Liechtenstein and Sidonie Elisabeth Altgräfin von Salm und Reifferscheidt. He was married on April 29, 1669 to Johanna Beatrix von Liechtenstein, they had 2 children. He was married on October  1, 1673 in Wilfersdorf to Eleonore Margarethe von Holstein-Sonderburg. He was married on April 21, 1703 to Maria Elisabeth von Liechtenstein. He died on April 21, 1709 in Krumau. This information is part of Genealogy Richard Remmé, The Hague, Netherlands by Richard Remmé on Genealogy Online.
data.text:
Personal data Maximilian von Liechtenstein

He was born on July 25, 1641 .

He died on April 21, 1709 in Krumau , he was 67 years old.

A child of Hartmann V Prinz von und zu Liechtenstein and Sidonie Elisabeth Altgräfin von Salm und Reifferscheidt

This information was last updated on December 4, 2022.

Household of Maximilian von Liechtenstein

(1) He is married to Johanna Beatrix von Liechtenstein.

They got married on April 29, 1669, he was 27 years old.

Child(ren):

(2) He is married to Eleonore Margarethe von Holstein-Sonderburg.

They got married on October 1, 1673 at Wilfersdorf, he was 32 years old.

(3) He is married to Maria Elisabeth von Liechtenstein.

They got married on April 21, 1703, he was 61 years old.
